header.gameNote: PAC-12 MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY NEW YORK LIFE - FINAL

videos.description: Tyler Dorsey steals inbounds pass and finishes with layup to give Oregon an 8-4 lead.
videos.headline: Dorsey gets steal and basket

videos.description: Arizona's Kadeem Allen drives baseline and finishes to tie the game at 10.
videos.headline: Allen drives to hoop for two

videos.description: Chance Comanche takes the feed from Allonzo Trier and dunks it home.
videos.headline: Comanche with the monster jam

videos.description: Dillon Brooks nails the 3-pointer from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Brooks drains the 3-pointer

videos.description: Chance Comanche feeds Dusan Ristic for the jam.
videos.headline: Arizona uses high-low pass for the dunk

videos.description: Oregon's Jordan Bell follows up the miss with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Bell with the one-handed jam

videos.description: Oregon's Kavell Bigby-Williams takes the pass from Payton Pritchard and slams it home.
videos.headline: Bigby-Williams throws it down

videos.description: Oregon's Kavell Bigby-Williams runs the court and sends the shot away.
videos.headline: Bigby-Williams with the huge block

videos.description: Sean Miller happy with play of front court players in 1st half.
videos.headline: Arizona head coach Sean Miller discusses 1st half action

videos.description: Arizona's Keanu Pinder takes the feed and finishes with one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Pinder opens up second half with the dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen converts the nice pass from Allonzo Trier with the big dunk
videos.headline: Markkanen powers it home

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier hits the desperation 3-pointer as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Trier beats the shot clock with long 3-pointer

videos.description: Oregon's Kavell Bigby-Williams blocks the shot and Dylan Ennis converts the layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Oregon turns defense into offense

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier takes it coast-to-coast for the basket.
videos.headline: Trier splits the defense for two

videos.description: Oregon's Jordan Bell skies for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Bell drives baseline for dunk

videos.description: Oregon's Dillon Brooks drains the clutch 3-pointer from the wing late in the second half against Arizona.
videos.headline: Brooks' three keeps Oregon alive

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier discusses the Wildcats' Pac-12 championship victory and believes that he and his team can go all the way.
videos.headline: Trier believes Wildcats have no ceiling

videos.description: Bill Walton and Dave Pasch break down Arizona's victory over Oregon in the Pac-12 championship and look to Allonzo Trier's impressive performance.
videos.headline: Trier was 'absolutely spectacular'

videos.description: Allonzo Trier scores 23 points to lead Arizona to an 83-80 win over Oregon to win the Pac-12 title.
videos.headline: Arizona holds on to top Oregon in Pac-12 final
